Biff Duncan Associates is a Information Technology consulting and professional services company that was founded in 2001 by a group of Information Technology consultants in Central New Jersey. The company started with the ideals of having second to none expertise, superior customer service, maximum quality of work, and complete customer satisfaction. As the company continues to grow, the staff at Biff Duncan continues to adhere to the core values on which Biff Duncan was founded.

Over the past few years we have served customers from various industries, such as manufacturing, financial services, health care services, education, and more. We at Biff Duncan pride ourselves on our ability to give personalized services and close personal attention to each and every customer.

In order to provide a total solution to our customers, we've partnered with technology companies that we feel are best-of-breed such as Cisco, HP, Citrix, Microsoft, VMware, Websense, Trend Micro, Barracuda and more. Our partner relationships allow us to enhance the end users customer experience with each of these vendors.
